description: After the no-confidence motion against the government was adjourned to March 28, Imran Khan's Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf has intensified efforts to woo its allies. But the renaming of the PM's official YouTube channel as well as a rally that is slated to take place on Sunday afternoon, have prompted speculation that Khan may step down as Prime Minister today.
